"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2532813\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2532813\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 14, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104urh1665702755394.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/urh1665702755394.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/urh1665702755394.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"urh1665702755394\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Creating a Web Output Filter Plug-in\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body taskbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Uniface provides a generic mechanism that enables you to add your own JavaScript or HTML to web pages generated from dynamic and static server pages.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section context\" id=\"urh1665702755394__context_w1217ab1b5b1_w1218ab1b5_w1219ab1\">\n<div class=\"div context\" id=\"urh1665702755394__topic_d22697e1_d22698e1_d22699e1\">\n</div>\n</section>\n<section><ol class=\"ol steps\"><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"urh1665702755394__li_d11114e1_d11115e1_d11116e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\" id=\"urh1665702755394__p_d22703e1_d22704e1_d22705e1\">Create a component that has an operation called\n                  <code class=\"ph codeph\">filterOutput</code>, with an IN parameter for the server page instance\n               name, and an INOUT parameter for the content to be injected into the server page. </span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<p class=\"p\">For example:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">operation filterOutput\nparams\n string pWebComponentInstanceName : In\n string pResponseStream : InOut\nendparams\n&lt;Your code here&gt;\nend ; operation filterOutput</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"urh1665702755394__p_d22706e1_d22707e1_d22708e1\">The UGOMEZ component contains useful\n                  functionality, for example, for reading parameters from an INI file, which you may\n                  wish to use as-is or adapt.</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"urh1665702755394__note_w1220ab1b5b3b1b3b7_w1221ab1b5b3b1b3_w1222ab1b5b3b1_w1223ab1b5b3_w1224ab1b5_w1225ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> The UGOMEZ component provides a caching mechanism that can be\n                  useful if you want to make your own component reusable. To make use of this, the\n                  component must be detached.</div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"urh1665702755394__p_d22709e1_d22710e1_d22711e1\">You are entirely free to implement the component\n                  as you see fit.</p>\n</div>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"urh1665702755394__li_d11117e1_d11118e1_d11119e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\" id=\"urh1665702755394__p_d22712e1_d22713e1_d22714e1\">Edit the application assignment file to add the\n               component name to the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">UWEBOUTPUTFILTERS</span> logical. </span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<p class=\"p\">For example:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[LOGICALS]\nUWEBOUTPUTFILTERS = myplugin</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"urh1665702755394__p_d22715e1_d22716e1_d22717e1\">The components defined by this logical are\n                  activated by the Uniface USYSHTTP component in the order specified by the logical,\n                  after it has generated the response to the browser request.</p>\n</div>\n</li></ol></section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qct1665702683487.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>USYSHTTP</a><p>The USYSHTTP component is a global web application request processor that handles all web requests sent to a Uniface Server via the Uniface Web Request Dispatcher (WRD).</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532813\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532813\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Creating a Web Output Filter Plug-in Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 14, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Creating a Web Output Filter Plug-in Uniface provides a generic mechanism that enables you to add your own JavaScript or HTML to web pages generated from dynamic and static server pages. Create a component that has an operation called filterOutput , with an IN parameter for the server page instance name, and an INOUT parameter for the content to be injected into the server page. For example: operation filterOutput params string pWebComponentInstanceName : In string pResponseStream : InOut endparams <Your code here> end ; operation filterOutput Copy The UGOMEZ component contains useful functionality, for example, for reading parameters from an INI file, which you may wish to use as-is or adapt. Note: The UGOMEZ component provides a caching mechanism that can be useful if you want to make your own component reusable. To make use of this, the component must be detached. You are entirely free to implement the component as you see fit. Edit the application assignment file to add the component name to the UWEBOUTPUTFILTERS logical. For example: [LOGICALS] UWEBOUTPUTFILTERS = myplugin Copy The components defined by this logical are activated by the Uniface USYSHTTP component in the order specified by the logical, after it has generated the response to the browser request. Related Links USYSHTTP The USYSHTTP component is a global web application request processor that handles all web requests sent to a Uniface Server via the Uniface Web Request Dispatcher (WRD). Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}